name: structured_v9_env_nested_mutation_with_branch_selected_rhs
section: binding-env-v9
args: p:Bool a:Int b:Int c:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Stress lexical environment lowering, shadowing, initializer order, and mutable variable lookup.
law: (= (with [x {a}] (do (if {p} (set! x (+ x {b})) (set! x (+ x {c}))) x)) (+ {a} (if {p} {b} {c})))
